Correction/Updating Personal Information<br/>
If a user's personally identifiable information changes (such as your zip code), or if a user no longer desires our service, we will endeavor to provide a way to correct, update or remove that user's personal data provided to us. This can usually be done at the member information page or by contacting us. <br/><br/>
Choice and Opt-out<br/>
